{"tid":1536191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點解完全無人理酷刑罪 仲好似習慣咗麻木咗","createTime":"2019-09-03T14:59:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T02:59:58.000Z","uid":177089,"like":69,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"06659867e4d3d38b5ba907a1a4be968fd9cbdccb","tid":1536191,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:59:52.000Z","msg":"執法人員喺執行職務期間 毆打被捕者令對方受到不必要傷害<br />\n已經係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">酷刑</span></span><br />\n係可以判<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">終身監禁</span></span><br />\n<br />\n就算香港法治理唔到 到國際上一樣係反人道行為<br />\n一樣係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">終身監禁</span></span><br />\n<br />\n點解香港人好似麻木咗咁？<br />\n由69到今日有過千人被無理暴力對待 甚至性侵犯<br />\n流血 斷骨 昏迷 嚴重受傷 甚至傳出死訊<br />\n而香港人係0途徑可以追究 甚或賠償<br />\n<br />\n點解到依家都唔發大呢件事 <br />\n仲未有一份受到整理嘅示威者受到嚴重暴力對待嘅文件<br />\n翻譯成英文 甚至各國語言 再不停更新 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">永不習慣</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">永不麻木</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">永不忘記</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">黑警暴力</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">追究到底</span></span><br />\n<br />\n誓要國際組織派員調查香港人道災難<br />\n將暴警送上國際法庭"},{"pid":"3d2a15a41f7bc3f4579cca539704a66b8f042ebe","tid":1536191,"uid":177089,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:00:45.000Z","msg":"依家根本唔係犯唔犯法 懷疑 捉咗入去打殘你<br />\n入到當bonus 入唔到都打殘咗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">拒絕麻木</span></span>"},{"pid":"82c03bffbdda7a248ef96b248cbd8b942defdadc","tid":1536191,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:01:15.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3cdbdbfa73473a3808fbd4296f0d072a577717da","tid":1536191,"uid":167883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:02:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Renq43y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRenq43y.jpg&h=bb73b46e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X2FTuve.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX2FTuve.jpg&h=3a22dffd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xbetioz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxbetioz.jpg&h=8f95a040&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1513398/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1513398/page/1</a><br />\n如何不仇警？"},{"pid":"be7d13e89e259e4d094b7e47431af84bb1316859","tid":1536191,"uid":264387,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"